                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4924,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/30/169033420/5e33c09fbd3c6781bb822fd9c57b6abc_7096377192318256652.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "純水精霊",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "純度が極めて高い水元素で形成された生命体で、先代水神エゲリアの眷属。カリロエーは純水精霊。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4539,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/29/224893084/1d1b81b0ff39641fa13df1528162b893_6433434114263866129.png",
                      "name": "フィンチじいさん",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "フィンチは幼少期にカリロエーと清泉町で出会う。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "交流するうちにフィンチは恋心を抱くが、人間と元素の精霊の時間の感覚の違いを懸念したカリロエーはフィンチから離れることを決意する。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "それから長い間フィンチはカリロエーとの再会を待ち望み、Ver.4.1限定イベント「流れゆく水に詩を紡いで」で遂に再会を果たす。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 44,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Diona_icon.png",
                      "name": "ディオナ",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ディオナが７歳になった日の夜、泉の精霊であるカリロエーは祝福を授ける。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "カリロエーから授かった祝福により、どんな酒でもディオナの手にかかると、たちまち想像もつかないほどの美酒となる。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "（キャラクター詳細、キャラクターストーリー5より）",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4906,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/04/237301566/c1060c024385e4bf2d87aa853d3a6afe_1315206165874795267.png",
                      "name": "Rhodeia",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 606,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/object/Endora_icon.png",
                      "name": "Endora",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3974,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/30/77454259/8f84efbb97c6667cbf39cb960acb5db8_8771159134506739723.png",
                      "name": "Idyia",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4604,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/12/01/151578876/b6d86ff8dfd84cf744e57a516b1a14c6_3541719482387705179.png",
                      "name": "Lyris",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "他の純水精霊。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
